{"tid":2047264,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國暴動》宵禁實施前 曼哈頓多間商店遭破窗洗劫","createTime":"2020-06-02T03:51:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-02T13:44:26.000Z","uid":141151,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"36d724a5cfada0f2b08ad2dc795c8a1b5c61df28","tid":2047264,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T03:51:05.000Z","msg":"美國暴動》宵禁實施前 曼哈頓多間商店遭破窗洗劫<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3184429\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3184429&d=Lcx8qPwugtyypLbLLwesbQHlXPv3B7QU%2BsV1%2BUkEKpk%3D&h=900426d7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3184429&h=45d72bab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3184429</a><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕佛洛伊德之死引發的示威抗議潮蔓延全美，甚至演變為多起破壞公物、洗劫商家的事件，迫使多個州政府實施宵禁。但就在宵禁令生效前，紐約曼哈頓多間商店遭人破窗洗劫，如入無人之境。<br />\n<br />\n《CNN》記者在紐約知名的聯合廣場目睹多起公然洗劫事件，無論是私人小店或是大型百貨都無法倖免，洗劫者丟擲公共單車、磚塊或用鐵鎚砸破店家玻璃窗，「我人就站在這裡，數名洗劫者就這樣進進出出，把東西拿走，還沒有半個警察到場」，記者指出，當下距離宵禁還有1個半小時，洗劫者便趕在時限前行動，且不只他人所在的現場，其他街區也有發生洗劫事件。<br />\n<br />\nCNN記者提到，其實鄰近的街區有警力部署，但洗劫者在得手後紛紛騎單車逃逸，躲避警方追緝。"},{"pid":"18bf404bdf14bb4dd2dd934a9b02c7c5e5e9c45b","tid":2047264,"uid":261937,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T03:54:11.000Z","msg":"continental hotel 好似都被爆"},{"pid":"190c6dde7f44eec1a81121d8ff8c392637daf2bb","tid":2047264,"uid":117679,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T04:06:51.000Z","msg":"紐約州州長做緊咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff5af23b98e6274fdd68dedf81426cf346dda8cd","tid":2047264,"uid":93649,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T04:08:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vr3LrRUfJsY&amp;t=1332s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dvr3LrRUfJsY